titleInfo.title: Koenig v. CBIZ Benefits&Insurance Services
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER - This matter is before the court on plaintiff Nancy Koenig's joint stipulation to release the bond in the District Court of Douglas County, Nebraska, 216. The court construes plaintiff's stipulation as a request that this court modify or dissolve the order from state court requiring the bond. See Filing No. 1, Attachment 1, pg. 25. As this case has settled, pursuant to 28 U.S.C. 1450, the court dissolves the state court order requiring posting of the bond. Ordered by Judge Joseph F. Bataillon.(JAE, )
